    // @description `string` the string value preceded by the `<alpha>` tag
    // @description ---
    //
    // @description **Links:**
    // @description [Text Mesh Pro: Rich Text Opacity](https://docs.unity3d.com/Packages/com.unity.textmeshpro@4.0/manual/RichTextOpacity.html)
    // @description ---
